          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/security/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">セキュリティ方針</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/code-of-conduct/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">行動規範</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/diversity-equity-inclusion/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">
