            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="border-t border-white/15 pt-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-2"
    >
      <span class="text-xs text-white/50">© {year} Contact, Inc. All rights reserved.</span>
      <span class="text-xs text-white/40 font-en">Founded 2022 in Karuizawa, Japan</span>
